value.0: The mysterious energies swirl around you...You are unsure of what is supposed to happen.

<StartAction>A strange, earthy sounding voice resounds in your ears...</Start>
"I am always before you, some distance away. Somewhere between land or sky. You may move towards me, yet distant I stay."

<StartAction>A strange, earthy sounding voice resounds in your ears...</Start>
"I hurt without moving. I poison without touching. I bear the honesty and the deceit. I am not to be judged by my size."

<StartAction>A strange, earthy sounding voice resounds in your ears...</Start>
"I am a mother and a father, but have never given birth. I am rarely still but I do not wander."

<StartAction>A strange, earthy sounding voice resounds in your ears...</Start>
"Give me subsistence and I shall live and grow. Give me water and I shall strink and die."

<StartAction>A strange, earthy sounding voice resounds in your ears...</Start>
"I fly when I am born. I lie when I am alive. I run when I am dead."

<StartAction>A strange, earthy sounding voice resounds in your ears...</Start>
"I live where the light falls. I scatter and die when the light is shined upon me."

<StartAction>A strange, earthy sounding voice resounds in your ears...</Start>
"Correct..."

<StartAction>A strange, earthy sounding voice resounds in your ears...</Start>
"...Wrong..."

<StartAction>A strange, earthy sounding voice resounds in your ears...</Start>
"I accept...Your gift..."
[Offer a small prayer to the Guardian...]
